{
  "name": "WorksheetView",
  "summary": "<p>通过使用 DisplayFormulas、DisplayGridlines 和 DisplayHeadings 等属性控制应用程序或工作簿级视图的外观和风格。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并隐藏第一个工作表视图的标题和网格线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHeadings</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayGridlines</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并显示第一个窗口的活动工作表视图的标题和零值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Windows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHeadings</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Windows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayDisplayZeros</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定的或活动工作簿中所有 <strong>WorksheetView</strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>您可以将此属性与 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表 ET 应用程序的 <a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application </a>对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表指定对象的创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayFormulas",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置在当前工作表视图中是显示还是隐藏公式。可读/写 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并显示活动工作表视图的公式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作簿1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormulas</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个窗口的活动工作表视图DisplayFormulas 属性的值设置为false。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Windows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayFormulas</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayGridlines",
      "summary": "<p>该属性仅适用于工作表和宏工作表。</p>\n<p>此属性仅影响显示的网格线。使用<strong>PrintGridlines</strong>属性可以控制网格线的打印。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果显示网格线，则为 <strong>True</strong>。可读/写 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并隐藏第一个工作表视图的网格线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作簿1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayGridlines</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一个窗口的活动工作表视图网格线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Windows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayGridlines</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayHeadings",
      "summary": "<p>该属性仅适用于工作表和宏工作表。</p>\n<p>此属性仅影响显示的标题。使用<strong>PrintHeadings</strong>属性可以控制标题的打印。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果同时显示行标题和列标题，则为 <strong>True</strong>；如果未显示标题，则为 <strong>False</strong>。可读/写 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例检查工作表视图是否显示行和列标题。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> view = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (view.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHeadings</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表视图显示行和列标题&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表视图不显示行和列标题&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并隐藏第一个工作表视图的标题。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHeadings</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayOutline",
      "summary": "<p>该属性仅适用于工作表和宏工作表。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果显示分级显示符号，则为 <strong>True</strong>。可读/写 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并隐藏第一个工作表视图的分级显示符号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayOutline</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例检查活动工作表视图是否显示分级显示符号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> view = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (view.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayOutline</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表视图显示分级显示符号&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表视图不显示分级显示符号&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayZeros",
      "summary": "<p>该属性仅适用于工作表和宏工作表。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果显示零值，则为 <strong>True</strong>。可读/写 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例激活工作表Sheet1，并隐藏第一个工作表视图的零值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayZeros</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例检查活动工作表视图是否显示零值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> view = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (view.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayZeros</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表视图显示零值&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;工作表视图不显示零值&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Sheet",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定<strong>WorksheetView</strong>对象的工作表对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表视图所在的工作表名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> activeSheetView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheetView</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`活动窗口的活动工作表视图所在的工作表为 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${activeSheetView.Sheet.Name}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例更改第一个工作表视图所在的工作表名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheetView = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWindow</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SheetViews</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sheetView.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;成绩表&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}